<define-tag description>denial of service</define-tag>
<define-tag moreinfo>
<p>A vulnerability was discovered in jabber, an instant messaging server,
whereby a bug in the handling of SSL connections could cause the
server process to crash, resulting in a denial of service.</p>

<p>For the current stable distribution (woody) this problem has been
fixed in version 1.4.2a-1.1woody1.</p>

<p>For the unstable distribution (sid) this problem has been fixed in
version 1.4.3-1.</p>

<p>We recommend that you update your jabber package.</p>
</define-tag>

